    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Implements consisting of a heavy head, usually of wood, with a handle or stock, used in various industrial and domestic operations, and having various shapes according to the purpose for which it is used. Examples include beetles for driving wedges or pegs, ramming down paving stones, or for crushing, bruising, beating, flattening, or smoothing various materials or things.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000027101/Smit, Means Illustrated Construction Dictionary (1985)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000114707/Oxford English Dictionary Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Grote houten voorhamers die worden gebruikt om pennen of wiggen te drijven, om zware houten balken op hun plaats te slaan of voor andere dingen waarbij het materiaal zou kunnen worden beschadigd wanneer er een gewone voorhamer werd gebruikt.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Großer Vorschlaghammer aus Holz, der zum Eintreiben von Pflöcken oder Keilen, zum Schlagen schwerer Holzbalken an ihren Platz oder bei anderen Anwendungen genutzt wird, wo Material Schaden erleiden könnte, wenn mit einem herkömmlichen Vorschlaghammer geschlagen wird.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000232/IfM-SMB-PK</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000122134/IfM Berlin</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
